  <generalInformation><![CDATA[<p>Whether its <a data-udi="umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald's</a> perfect beginners' nursery slopes at Bodmi, through the long scenic, tree-lined runs on 'First', <a data-udi="umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730}" title="Wengen">Wengen's</a> satisfying red runs at Kleine Scheidegg, or <a data-udi="umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc}" title="Murren">Mürren's</a> more challenging mogul fields up at Schilthorn, the <a data-udi="umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656}" title="Jungfrau Ski Region">Jungfrau area</a> really does have something for everyone - all with the Eiger, Mönch and Jungfrau trio as a spectacular backdrop.</p>]]></generalInformation>
